 2024-08352024-06-21AAFC
ActFarm Income Protection Act
SubjectOrder Authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to Enter into an Agreement with Quebec Under Subsection 12(5) of the Farm Income Protection Act (Horticultural Producers)
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into an AGREEMENT with Quebec to provide federal contributions of up to $13.34 million under the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program (AgriRecovery) to assist horticultural producers with the extraordinary costs incurred as a result of excess rainfall during the summer of 2023.
AttachmentsAttachment
